node.text: Hudson was wondering why his bike was fish tailing 😅 New video live on our YouTube channel The Deegan’s 🤘🏻 #thedeegans #moto @shopdeegan38

Met a kid who watches our YouTube channel. He says it’s motivating. So I spent some time talking to him asking him what his plans are for life and listen to his dreams. You never know there is usually one or multiple people in your life that have said something along the way that motivated you to push forward and succeed. Everyone has feelings emotions and dreams sometimes you just have to be a good listener and let them speak it to verify there plan. It’s funny the other kids at the car wash were poking fun at him but he’s the one that made a connection that could possibly lead to advancing in line. Good luck bud with your goals don’t let anyone put doubt in you ! #TheDeegans #behindthescenes
